{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hello and welcome to Kaisa: Resurrection! We\u2019re a small two-man team working hard to bring this game to life. Throw us a wishlist and support our journey to the finish line!</strong><br><br>Bound to fulfill your master\u2019s bidding, you play as a newly reanimated being. After the sun sets and the clock strikes midnight, your task begins: you must feed your master before the first light of dawn. How hard can it possibly be to survive the night?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What happens during the day?... Well, that's another story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feed your master during the night.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scheme &amp; Prepare during the day.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find or order mighty weapons like REGULAR chopsticks or UNIMPRESSIVE kitchen knifes to improve your combat abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Who knew lies could be a currency.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stuff your master to turn back time.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beware the noise you make, for that which listens will come..</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not everything is as it seems.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739322085","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025870/page.bg.jpg?t=1739322085","capsule_image":"https://sha